{{Nesiseri aatikl}}
'''Maaxizim''' a wah metad a suoshoikanamik analisis, we arijiniet frah di migl-tu-liet 19t senchri wok a Joerman filasafa Kaal Maax ([[Karl Marx]]) ah Friijrik Engglz (Friedrich Engels), we analaiz klaas rilieshan ah sasayatal kanflik bai yuuz matiirialis intopritieshan a istarikal divelopment ah dayalektikal vyuu a suoshal chranzfamieshan.

